snippet.title: AMBER HEARD Files SANCTION Against JOHNNY DEPP's Lawyer For TWEETS
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has filed a sanction in the Virginia trial against Johnny Depp's Lawyer Adam Waldman for tweets!! 
The hypocrisy from Amber Heard and her team is hilarious!

Adam Waldman continues to destroy them with short epic tweets and Johnny Depp must be laughing in the background at how his Lawyer is defending him.

Thanks for watching!!
